txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the merrevail, Orcs, and other intelligent creatures near Gath Forthnír. Deilvery of the items should be made to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-outpost.
'We could use the broken weapons from the intelligent enemies surrounding us. Get them for us.'
Council of the North Task: Broken Wooden Clubs
The Rangers at Gath Forthnír await a delivery of broken wooden clubs to be made to Areneth.
Deliver the broken wooden clubs to Areneth at Gath Forthnír in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver broken wooden clubs from the sentient creatures near Gath Forthnír to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-camp.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the merrevail, Orcs, and other intelligent creatures near Gath Forthnír.
